      <event start="T1289-813" end="T380">eem </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T1292-907">sem giros probala. </event>
      <event start="T1292-907" end="T1295-826">To je k tak mal boljši kebab. </event>
      <event start="T1295-826" end="T1296-736">Če b tko rekla. </event>
      <event start="T1296-736" end="T1298-397">A si že probu? </event>
