      <event start="T218-473" end="T222-508">[glas] eem pa iz te() s tega vidika izkoristiti otok. </event>
      <event start="T222-508" end="T225-214">Eem ... [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T225-214" end="T61">in ja, </event>
      <event start="T61" end="T62">smo pol, </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T230-24">se mi, da smo kar [zvok] v redu eee balansirali, </event>
